title: Easy Social Share Buttons for WordPress v3.2.1 - WP Plugins
description:
Easy Social Share Buttons for WordPress is all-in-one social sharing plugin or WordPress that allows you share, monitor and increase your social popularity. With Easy Social Share Buttons for WordPress you will take your social sharing & following on a next level. Contains external links.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
